Late Nite Chef Fight - Season 2, Episode 1




Skin and Bones

A high-end maestro of Southern comfort food goes up against a Filipino catering firecracker, as a primal battle of the sexes heats up in the Palms parking lot. Without help from their staffs and at the mercy of whatever these trucks have on-hand, will these culinary wizards be able to save their own skin?
